divs: Sighting DetailsI WAS LETTING MY DOGS OUT AND I HAPPENED TO LOOK AT THE SKY AND I SAW BIG DIPPER AND LITTLE DIPPER THEN THIS WHAT APPEARED TO BE A STAR WENT BY THE BIG DIPPER THEN THROUGH THE LITTEL DIPPER BLINKED AND WENT ACROSS THE SKY THEN UP AND DOWN THEN APPEARED TO GO DECEND STRAIGHT DOWN TOWARDS THE OCEAN AS I LIVE BY THE HYANNIS HARBOR. IT WAS SILENT, I COMMENTED TO MYSELF WHAT THE HELL IS THAT THAT WOKE MY DAUGHTER WHO IT FIRST TH0UGHT IT WAS A COMET OR FALLING STAR BUT THEY WAY IT MOVED IT COULD HAVE NOT BEEN, I CALL MY LOCAL AIRPORT AND THEY HAD NO REPORTS AND NOT SURE WHERE I SHOULD REPORT SO I AM REPORTING IT TO YOU. NOT SURE WHAT IT WAS, BUT I MADE ME FEEL UNEASY.
Summary: LOOKED LIKE STAR BUT WENT ACROSS THE SKY BLINKED THEN UP AND DOWN THEN DESENDING DOWN UNTIL; OUT OF MY EYE SIGHT CALL THE LOCAY AIRPORT DOWN PLANS OR SIGHTINGS
